    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2003-06-19</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2003-10-23T20:21:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Veterans Affairs Reorganization Act of 2003 - Establishes in the Department of Veterans Affairs an Office of Homeless Veterans Assistance Programs. Directs the Secretary of Veterans Affairs, through the Office Director, to carry out all Department homeless veterans assistance functions and programs.</p> <p>Transfers to the Secretary all functions of the Secretary of Labor under the homeless veterans reintegration program and requires the Secretary to carry out such functions through the Office.</p> <p>Directs the Archivist of the United States to transfer to the Secretary operational responsibility for the Military Personnel Records facility of the National Personnel Records Center, St. Louis, Missouri.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
